summary:
Winner of the Universities of Strasbourg Prize for Doctoral Thesis, 2004;
Winner of a Publication Grant by competition (University of Strasbourg, 2008).

Reviewed in: 
Revue de Linguistique Romane 77 (2013): 549-552 by A. Variano;
Studi linguistici italiani 37/1 (2011): 142-144 by G. Polimeni; 
Lingua e stile 46 (2011): 313-316 by M. Aprile; 
Italica 88/1 (2011): 155-156 by C. Damnotti; 
Lingua Nostra 3/4 (2010):126-127 by A. Dardi.
